Individual




Dirk Jungé



Mr. Dirk Jungé, CFA, is Independent Director at L.B. Foster Co., Independent Director at Paramount Resources Ltd., Chairman at The Pitcairn Trust Co., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Pitcairn Financial Group, Inc., a Member at Financial Planning Association, and a Member at CFA Institute. He is on the Board of Directors at L.B. Foster Co., The Freeman Cos., Paramount Resources Ltd., and The National Philanthropic Trust.
Mr. Jungé was previously employed as Chairman by Pitcairn Group LP.
He received his undergraduate degree from Lehigh University.



